	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Isn't a practial one, and probably not very original one. It just somehow get into my head and I thought to share.<br /><br />It does not require anything special, but comes with drawbacks - now there is limitation 8 sprites per column, and it is not very compatible with existing games.<br /><br />So, what are the steps to perform the mod:<br /><br />1) Turn your TV screen 90 degrees to a side.<br /><br />Alternative version:<br /><br />1) Tilt your head 90 degress to a side.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
