	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you want to have a Dhalsim arm that extends horizontally, the background's probably the best way to do it so that you don't get flicker like with the Magnet Beam in the original <em>Mega Man</em>. As for using it while jumping, you could change the angle if it's used in the air, like <em>Smash Bros.</em> series does for Ness's PK Fire (front B). But your backgrounds may have to be simple so that you don't get attribute clash when the arm extends over them.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
